title: Episode 13: Annie F. Downs
description:
Season 2 of Coffee with Kailey is here! On today's episode, Kailey sits down with her good friend Annie F. Downs. They talk about just a bit of everything, from actively choosing disciplines & creating habits, to advice on dating & how to find true community with honest friendships.


Thank you to our show's sponsors!
